{"word":"G657 - ἀποτάσσομαι - apotássomai - ap-ot-as'-som-ahee - Bid farewell","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀποτάσσομαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">apotássomai</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ap-ot-as'-som-ahee</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Bid farewell</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - அனுப்பு, வெறுத்துவிடு, உத்தரவு பெறு, அனுப்புவி"},{"paragraph":"to set apart, to separate"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Middle voice from <a href=\"#/G575 - ἀπό - apó - apo'/575\">G575</a> and <a href=\"#/G5021 - τάσσω - tássō - tas'-so/5021\">G5021</a>; literally to <i>say adieu</i> (by departing or dismissing); figuratively to <i>renounce:</i> - bid farewell, forsake, take leave, send away.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1296/1296\">G1296</a>, <a href=\"#/G1297/1297\">G1297</a>, <a href=\"#/G1299/1299\">G1299</a>, <a href=\"#/G2004/2004\">G2004</a>, <a href=\"#/G392/392\">G392</a>, <a href=\"#/G4367/4367\">G4367</a>, <a href=\"#/G5001/5001\">G5001</a>, <a href=\"#/G5021/5021\">G5021</a>, <a href=\"#/G506/506\">G506</a>, <a href=\"#/G5292/5292\">G5292</a>, <a href=\"#/G5293/5293\">G5293</a>, <a href=\"#/G657/657\">G657</a>, <a href=\"#/G812/812\">G812</a>, <a href=\"#/G813/813\">G813</a>, <a href=\"#/G814/814\">G814</a>"}]}